Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,かき消すためか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:49.87,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.12,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,That's right.
